{"tid":2252093,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美媒獲維修簽名單 證電腦屬亨特","createTime":"2020-10-21T09:00:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-21T10:19:20.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d4c4055a8b49e040aa8c906fa8b4fc7ac4c832ad","tid":2252093,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T09:00:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20201021/ITSTVCO7GRF5FPVQ7VHKN2YJTQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201021%2FITSTVCO7GRF5FPVQ7VHKN2YJTQ%2F&d=z3Qy88JfdbGSADH60DObPZuyGkzLGvEkvhYecc72uXM%3D&h=1ffab555\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201021%2FITSTVCO7GRF5FPVQ7VHKN2YJTQ%2F&h=ed51fed5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20201021/ITSTVCO7GRF5FPVQ7VHKN2YJTQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n美媒獲維修簽名單 證電腦屬亨特<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/i6KLqbvNLzscYOt9dC32NKj14mk=/720x516/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/DTBHUEEEEBHC7KKR2IBJZCCCUE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fi6KLqbvNLzscYOt9dC32NKj14mk%3D%2F720x516%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FDTBHUEEEEBHC7KKR2IBJZCCCUE.jpg&h=4249e3ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n亨特<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。。，但美國霍士新聞取得亨特將電腦送修的簽名單據，證明電郵來自的手提電腦，確實屬於亨特本人。<br />\n<br />\n霍士新聞取得有關電腦在特拉華州送修的文件單據，發單的是威爾明頓「The Mac Shop」，單據列明三部蘋果MacBook Pro手提電腦整修詳情，開單對象一欄寫有亨特拜登名字，顯示維修費用為85美元（663港元） 。但顧客簽名是否出於亨特本人之手，有待確認。<br />\n<br />\n霍士亦取得該店店東艾薩克（John Paul Mac Isaac）向聯邦調查局（FBI）報案等相關文件，包。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n情報總監指沒證據俄主使<br />\n<br />\n有民主黨人日前聲言，所謂亨特電郵門是俄羅斯散播假消息以打擊拜登選情；50名前情報高官包括中情局（FBI）幾位前局長，前日聯署發表信件，指拜登電郵外洩一事，「充滿俄羅斯散播假資訊行動的一貫特點」。但國家情報總監拉特克里夫前日接受訪問，已表明沒證據顯示這是俄羅斯抹黑行動。<br />\n<br />\n另外，霍士新聞披露facebook、Twitter人員與拜登團隊過從甚密，。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n美國霍士新聞網站/德新社"},{"pid":"24a149502f541d3a1239eda53cd5039cf932a2fb","tid":2252093,"uid":100155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T09:47:46.000Z","msg":"［美國版721］［極醜惡］受害者tweeter account被滅聲<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2249542\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2249542</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"138c2ab5de27af9c4071ed21e0f2bf4e7334c9f7","tid":2252093,"uid":81113,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T10:02:22.000Z","msg":"又一個冇五毛post<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3186767dce887ccdf7ab00a336068a9e314ec58f","tid":2252093,"uid":179311,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T10:19:20.000Z","msg":"好似永遠都只係得fox nyp sypport<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}